NOTICE — Derivative work acknowledgement

This project is a derivative work. The immediate upstream of src/IME.ahk
is the AutoHotkey v2 port by Ken'ichiro Ayaki (k-ayaki), published on
2023-07-17 and declared NYSL <http://www.kmonos.net/nysl/> at that time.
NYSL explicitly permits free modification and relicensing (section A-3 /
A-4), so this fork is MIT-licensed.

This project combines two independent upstream lineages that converge in
yuki0ueda/alt-ime-rev:

  src/IME.ahk (IME control library):
    eamat                      — original AutoHotkey v1 version, distributed as "089.zip" (2008-09-21) via http://lukewarm.s101.xrea.com/up/. GitHub: @eamat-dot
    Ken'ichiro Ayaki (k-ayaki) — AutoHotkey v2 port at https://github.com/k-ayaki/IMEv2.ahk (NYSL declared at publication, 2023-07-17)
    yuki0ueda (this repo)      — fork modifications: error handling, automatic retry, file logging with 10MB rotation, ARM64 pointer-width fixes

  src/alt-ime-rev.ahk (main hotkey script):
    karakaram                  — original AutoHotkey v1 "alt-ime-ahk" at https://github.com/karakaram/alt-ime-ahk
    nekocodeX                  — intermediate fork "alt-ime-ahk-mod", formerly at github.com/nekocodeX/alt-ime-ahk-mod (repository no longer available)
    yuki0ueda (this repo)      — AutoHotkey v2 fork at https://github.com/yuki0ueda/alt-ime-rev (current maintainer)
